  "title": "Crowd Pleased Malaysian Gorgonzola-dolce Bisque Mini Cocotte",
  "description": "A rich and creamy Malaysian-inspired bisque with gorgonzola dolce, served in individual mini cocotte. Perfect as a crowd-pleasing snack or dessert.",
